  "remarks": "\nQods Aeronautics Industries (QAI) is an involved person within the meaning of the Iran (Sanctions) (Nuclear) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019. Qods Aeronautics Industries (QAI) is or has been   responsible for, providing support for or facilitating a relevant nuclear activity, specifically the development of a nuclear weapon delivery system in, or for use in, Iran.",
